              "type": "json",
              "data": "{}"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Updates additional information for an EOR employee agreement. Only works if the employee’s contract status is new, under_review, or waiting_for_employee_contract. Using other statuses can cause errors.\n **Token scopes**: `worker:write`"
