                "description": "The ID of the worker whose payslip download link is being requested."
              },
              {
                "name": "payslip_id",
                "value": "",
                "type": "path",
                "description": "The ID of the specific payslip to download."
              }
            ]
          },
          "docs": "Retrieve a URL to download a specific payslip PDF for a EoR worker. This endpoint is useful for accessing detailed payment records in a portable document format.\n **Token scopes**: `payslips:read`"
        }
